{"tid":452223,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"成日話5-6周無限貨","createTime":"2017-10-30T03:30:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-30T08:30:23.000Z","uid":127764,"like":13,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"2aa3d98e1b3af4bf3222a3c10c9525e04603d5f8","tid":452223,"uid":127764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T03:30:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不嬲都係早買早享受 遲買平幾舊<br />\n如果全部人都唔care遲拎機，一早已經無炒機呢樣野<br />\nAOS撚學咩人炒機，咁撚遲仲諗住有得炒<br />\n要炒就ir!<br />\n<br />\n理撚得你5-6weeks無限貨！第一日有機先好講野！"},{"pid":"c855776ca10c9e4567d271d6db92db8f53c1156f","tid":452223,"uid":20998,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T03:32:18.000Z","msg":"啱呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6abf73143a6136fde1d49f14032c0fe9ca417f3d","tid":452223,"uid":61463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T03:32:32.000Z","msg":"真 利伸 頭批機"},{"pid":"ce206758b6eb529b2e0ae5b02a25a4b69ee434cd","tid":452223,"uid":127764,"like":3,"dislike":8,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T03:37:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/30/113709_e59124f8f2a9d4333dedd82f43876521.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F30%2F113709_e59124f8f2a9d4333dedd82f43876521.jpg&h=db677d14&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"88a7a041bd04d9f2cb917a5408627c72c2cbc4ac","tid":452223,"uid":61864,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T04:05:10.000Z","msg":"今時唔同往日啊<br />\n唔通重有得炒成個月咩"},{"pid":"58779ca9bbb85785c5c19c3f9d45910c883d2921","tid":452223,"uid":3302,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T04:06:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>今時唔同往日啊<br />\n唔通重有得炒成個月咩</blockquote><br />\n呢d 留言真係要mark低星期五推返上黎鞭屍"},{"pid":"93142961ccd9f21120d8f5fefddde78505f1082e","tid":452223,"uid":127764,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T04:09:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>今時唔同往日啊<br />\n唔通重有得炒成個月咩</blockquote><br />\n所以我咪話除左ir既唔好諗炒機<br />\nAos5-6weeks無限貨對ir無衝突"},{"pid":"711eceab41a0f040355a972ae42c59b7c1be0e26","tid":452223,"uid":127764,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T04:12:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>今時唔同往日啊<br />\n唔通重有得炒成個月咩</blockquote><br />\n所以我咪話除左ir既唔好諗炒機<br />\nAos5-6weeks無限貨對ir無衝突</blockquote><br />\n當我要拎部機出黎威！要型 人無我有<br />\n明知幾個星期後周街都有機<br />\n我要快人一步有，咪比貴啲炒價<br />\n唔要型既，都唔會買呢部咁貴啦<br />\n理論上如果ir少貨，今次無限貨仲會直線推高頭幾日個價<br />\n仲要ir同aos無撞期"},{"pid":"c9e8540211c1576d2b8358edba8944bd6df17d59","tid":452223,"uid":77515,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T04:13:39.000Z","msg":"3號IR收完第一批，到18號前日日都有IR<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nAOS第一批都<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"518833b00225753e203d9248cee892517c7df9ad","tid":452223,"uid":127764,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T04:15:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>3號IR收完第一批，到18號前日日都有IR<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nAOS第一批都<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n第一批aos都會有一千幾百，但遲成3星期出貨就要有自用心態，如果幾舊水都輸唔起既就cut單"},{"pid":"b759c4c5600790f0ef48004c9d108d335e204d7c","tid":452223,"uid":75372,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T04:17:05.000Z","msg":"3-4就有水位既,5-6就不了"},{"pid":"0a62b862d54eb6ca4af0c4b2fe2cacdef6f88063","tid":452223,"uid":127764,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T04:20:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>3-4就有水位既,5-6就不了</blockquote><br />\n5-6開始應該會維持3k附近<br />\n睇出貨量有幾多，同埋先達佬接唔接到訂單，如果先達佬接左單，個日出貨量又少既，高過第一日都唔出奇"},{"pid":"ae495e3fda4bdf4a403227ef4a3c4bb7557bd978","tid":452223,"uid":23011,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T06:30:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/30/113709_e59124f8f2a9d4333dedd82f43876521.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F30%2F113709_e59124f8f2a9d4333dedd82f43876521.jpg&h=db677d14&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n夜晚先拎機都好意思show出黎威<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我自己朝早11點都覺得遲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2447a6c1deaf90d842b31ff15e3745cb06ae4e32","tid":452223,"uid":153049,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T06:33:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/30/143242_2a61d6cc0cbb2f667fb997d6c6283f87.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F30%2F143242_2a61d6cc0cbb2f667fb997d6c6283f87.jpg&h=3adf6615&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有無得再早d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eca7fd07d59f46c7288b43941d70573bdb32aeff","tid":452223,"uid":44162,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T06:49:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/30/144900_3f9e5e9b5547330e261a3e3facaee10b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F30%2F144900_3f9e5e9b5547330e261a3e3facaee10b.png&h=de7f29ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我係AOS撚<br />\n不過自用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d069eb8a6eac7c4fd7ecbf3773468161c5d4f60","tid":452223,"uid":127764,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T07:43:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/30/143242_2a61d6cc0cbb2f667fb997d6c6283f87.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnai